    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J410">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The first Day's Night had come --</l>
                    <l>And grateful that a thing</l>
                    <l>So terrible -- had been endured --</l>
                    <l>I told my Soul to sing --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>She said her Strings were snapt --</l>
                    <l>Her Bow -- to Atoms blown --</l>
                    <l>And so to mend her -- gave me work</l>
                    <l>Until another Morn --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And then -- a Day as huge</l>
                    <l>As Yesterdays in pairs,</l>
                    <l>Unrolled it's horror in my face --</l>
                    <l>Until it blocked my eyes --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>My Brain -- begun to laugh --</l>
                    <l>I mumbled -- like a fool --</l>
                    <l>And tho' 'tis Years ago -- that Day --</l>
                    <l>My Brain keeps giggling -- still.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And Something's odd -- within --</l>
                    <l>That person that I was --</l>
                    <l>And this One -- do not feel the same --</l>
                    <l>Could it be Madness -- this?</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
